[[File:Invisible_Hand_holograph.png|thumb|250px|A holograph of the [[Invisible Hand/Legends|''Invisible Hand'']]]]
A '''holograph''' was a static three-dimensional image.

==Description==
A holograph was a static three-dimensional image,<ref name="CSWE-holograph">{{CSWECite|II|52|holograph}}</ref> whereas a [[Hologram/Legends|hologram]] was a moving three-dimensional image that could be broadcast in real [[Time/Legends|time]] as part of a communication transmission.<ref name="CSWE-hologram">{{CSWECite|II|52|hologram}}</ref>

==History==
Holographs were utilized in a variety of ways, including briefing soldiers on the location of a hostage<ref name="ROTS">{{Film|III}}</ref> or planning an infiltration route.<ref name="TPM">{{Film|I}}</ref>

Souvenir holographs could be bought on [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] for 10 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].<ref name="GG2">[[Galaxy Guide 2: Yavin and Bespin (Second Edition)|''Galaxy Guide 2: Yavin and Bespin'', Second Edition]]</ref>

